1. Create the `Commit.convention` file with conventional commit standards
2. Document the `.convention` context file type in `Planning/ContextFiles.md`
3. Update workspace file associations to treat `.convention` as markdown
4. Ensure convention files are discoverable and referenced in delegation prompts

